      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is the regulatory-accepted metric for comparative hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. CFD computes RH via the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model integrated along Lagrangian particle tracks. Direct correspondence between computational QoI and clinical decision criterion confirmed by clinical expert review."
